title: 10 Takeaways from Week 6
itunes:title: 10 Takeaways from Week 6
description:
Six straight weeks with an overtime game and a SNF thriller, what more can you ask for?! DJ and Bucky share 10 takeaways from the weekend that was, including the Chiefs and Pats SNF epic was a playoff preview (:30), Oakland’s phone lines are open for trades (7:00), no need to BYOS (Bring Your Own Sacks) to the Ravens’ party (16:00), Sam Darnold continues to improve (19:00) and a balanced offense is the key to Pittsburgh’s success (26:50)
